Hey, we're the police.

1026
01:06:20.527 --> 01:06:22.596
You're the police?

1027
01:06:24.698 --> 01:06:25.832
[**]

1028
01:06:25.865 --> 01:06:27.801
Police?

1029
01:06:30.670 --> 01:06:32.972
And you saved us.

1030
01:06:33.006 --> 01:06:35.475
MALE OFFICER:
All right.


1031
01:06:35.509 --> 01:06:39.846
Thank you. Thank you.

1032
01:06:39.879 --> 01:06:41.415
Gina.

1033
01:06:42.582 --> 01:06:44.551
Gina, they found us.
We're free.


1034
01:06:51.291 --> 01:06:53.427
I'm Georgina DeJesus.

1035
01:06:56.763 --> 01:07:01.668
Oh, my Lord. I've been looking
for you for nine years.


1036
01:07:03.169 --> 01:07:04.438
MALE OFFICER:
Let's get you out of here.


1037
01:07:04.471 --> 01:07:05.805
MICHELLE:
No, no.


1038
01:07:05.839 --> 01:07:07.907
Please, he could show up
and kill us.


1039
01:07:07.941 --> 01:07:09.643
It's okay,
I won't let you go.


1040
01:07:09.676 --> 01:07:11.645
You're safe, it's over.

1041
01:07:11.678 --> 01:07:13.146
[**]

1042
01:07:13.179 --> 01:07:16.049
One seventeen to base.
DISPATCHER: Go, 117.


1043
01:07:16.082 --> 01:07:20.287
MALE OFFICER:
We found them. We found them.


1044
01:08:11.271 --> 01:08:13.206
[INAUDIBLE DIALOGUE]

1045
01:08:54.448 --> 01:08:55.849
[CHUCKLES]

1046
01:08:55.882 --> 01:08:57.984
I'm coming home, Joey!

1047
01:08:58.017 --> 01:09:01.655
I'm free! We're free!

1048
01:09:05.258 --> 01:09:07.193
[SOBBING]

1049
01:09:16.603 --> 01:09:19.739
REPORTER 1:
All three women were rescued
from a home just now.


1050
01:09:19.773 --> 01:09:21.475
REPORTER 2:
An absolutely unbelievable
story.


1051
01:09:21.508 --> 01:09:24.043
REPORTER 3:
It was a night full
of emotion and drama.


1052
01:09:24.077 --> 01:09:26.045
REPORTER 4:
They were missing
for more than...


1053
01:09:26.079 --> 01:09:27.481
REPORTER 5:
--screams from a nearby house.


1054
01:09:27.514 --> 01:09:29.015
REPORTER 6:
They also found
Michelle Knight,


1055
01:09:29.048 --> 01:09:32.519
who went missing in 2002.

1056
01:09:32.552 --> 01:09:35.489
WOMAN [OVER PA]:
Paging Dr. Adler.
Please come to X-ray.


1057
01:09:35.522 --> 01:09:37.757
NURSE: Hydrate.
Dr. Adler to X-ray.


1058
01:09:37.791 --> 01:09:41.428
No men, no men. Only women.
Okay, men, out.


1059
01:09:43.162 --> 01:09:47.133
On my count,
three, two, one, go.


1060
01:09:47.166 --> 01:09:49.869
Let's go.

1061
01:09:49.903 --> 01:09:51.304
I wanna see my son.

1062
01:09:51.337 --> 01:09:53.206
I want him to know
I'm alive, please.


1063
01:10:01.548 --> 01:10:04.250
CARLA:
Well, look who's awake.


1064
01:10:04.283 --> 01:10:07.821
Good morning.
How do you feel?


1065
01:10:07.854 --> 01:10:09.756
REPORTER [ON TV]:
Three men are now in custody.


1066
01:10:09.789 --> 01:10:12.692
It smells so clean.

1067
01:10:12.726 --> 01:10:14.561
So clean.

1068
01:10:16.963 --> 01:10:18.665
I wanna see my son.

1069
01:10:18.698 --> 01:10:20.800
DOCTOR:
Do you know
where we can contact him?


1070
01:10:20.834 --> 01:10:23.570
I don't know.

1071
01:10:23.603 --> 01:10:27.641
He went into a foster home
right before he took--


1072
01:10:27.674 --> 01:10:29.075
He took me.

1073
01:10:29.108 --> 01:10:32.145
Do you think anybody here
could help me?


1074
01:10:32.178 --> 01:10:34.881
Don't worry.
We'll look into it for you.


1075
01:10:36.650 --> 01:10:40.219
Is there any family
we can call for you?


1076
01:10:42.822 --> 01:10:47.226
Nobody that wouldn't know how
to find me if they wanted to.


1077
01:10:47.260 --> 01:10:48.995
The other girls
returned home.


1078
01:10:49.028 --> 01:10:50.964
Amanda Berry's family
lets us know


1079
01:10:50.997 --> 01:10:53.667
her and her daughter
are doing well.


1080
01:10:53.700 --> 01:10:55.802
They ask that we give them
their privacy


1081
01:10:55.835 --> 01:10:57.904
for this time of healing
and recovery.


1082
01:10:57.937 --> 01:10:59.639
And in other news.

1083
01:10:59.673 --> 01:11:02.476
Oh, my.
Hello.


1084
01:11:02.509 --> 01:11:05.211
Oh, my goodness.
Would you look at all that?


1085
01:11:05.244 --> 01:11:07.647
I swear, we need to give
some of this away.


1086
01:11:07.681 --> 01:11:10.283
Yes.
Except for this one.


1087
01:11:10.316 --> 01:11:11.518
What a cutie.

1088
01:11:11.551 --> 01:11:15.188
Aww. Joey would love this.

1089
01:11:17.190 --> 01:11:21.695
I keep forgetting
that Joey's almost 16 now.


1090
01:11:23.229 --> 01:11:26.232
I wonder if I would even
recognize him at this point


1091
01:11:26.265 --> 01:11:28.735
or if he would remember me.
Yeah.


1092
01:11:28.768 --> 01:11:30.804
WOMAN:
Can I see her?


1093
01:11:30.837 --> 01:11:33.507
CARLA:
Excuse me. Excuse me.


1094
01:11:36.843 --> 01:11:41.414
Uh, Jake Solano, FBI.

1095
01:11:41.447 --> 01:11:43.950
Can we talk for a minute?
Is that all right?


1096
01:11:46.419 --> 01:11:48.454
Jake Solano, FBI?

1097
01:11:48.488 --> 01:11:50.957
I think the doctors
promised you something


1098
01:11:50.990 --> 01:11:53.693
once you were cleared
for solid food?


1099
01:11:53.727 --> 01:11:56.530
MICHELLE:
Mm.


1100
01:11:56.563 --> 01:11:58.765
A cheeseburger from
Steak 'n Shake?


1101
01:11:58.798 --> 01:12:00.767
Mm-hm. With triple fries

1102
01:12:00.800 --> 01:12:04.403
and a cheesecake Blizzard
from Dairy Queen.


1103
01:12:10.510 --> 01:12:12.579
[LAUGHS]
Thank you.


1104
01:12:16.616 --> 01:12:18.985
Oh, my God.

1105
01:12:19.018 --> 01:12:21.888
You are an angel

1106
01:12:21.921 --> 01:12:25.625
a million times over. Mm.

1107
01:12:25.659 --> 01:12:28.628
Mm. Mm.

1108
01:12:28.662 --> 01:12:29.996
[GROANS]

1109
01:12:30.029 --> 01:12:32.331
I think I better not rush it.

1110
01:12:32.365 --> 01:12:33.700
Oh, here.

1111
01:12:33.733 --> 01:12:35.434
Whoa. Whoa, whoa.

1112
01:12:35.468 --> 01:12:38.572
I'm sorry, I didn't mean
to frighten you.


1113
01:12:38.605 --> 01:12:40.273
It's okay.

1114
01:12:40.306 --> 01:12:42.942
I'm sorry.

1115
01:12:42.976 --> 01:12:44.811
[**]

1116
01:12:49.115 --> 01:12:51.951
You know, whenever
he wanted me to shut up


1117
01:12:51.985 --> 01:12:57.356
he would put that kind
of napkin down my throat.


1118
01:13:00.827 --> 01:13:04.463
I just wanna find my son.
Have you found my son?


1119
01:13:04.497 --> 01:13:07.901
Not yet, but trust me,
we're-- We're on it.


1120
01:13:15.341 --> 01:13:18.277
Michelle?
Oh, hey.


1121
01:13:18.311 --> 01:13:20.413
Sorry.

1122
01:13:20.446 --> 01:13:22.448
Your mother's here.

1123
01:13:27.153 --> 01:13:30.156
Can you please tell her
that I'm not up for it today?


1124
01:13:32.025 --> 01:13:36.362
Actually, please tell her
that I don't want to see her


1125
01:13:36.395 --> 01:13:38.598
or else she's gonna keep
coming back.


1126
01:13:38.632 --> 01:13:40.099
Are you sure?

1127
01:13:40.133 --> 01:13:43.469
Carla, you've seen parents
of missing children, right?


1128
01:13:44.904 --> 01:13:48.307
They keep the kids'
bedrooms intact


1129
01:13:48.341 --> 01:13:51.044
as if they never went
missing


1130
01:13:51.077 --> 01:13:53.647
or they keep their voice
on the voicemail


1131
01:13:53.680 --> 01:13:56.349
so they can listen to
their kid's voice again


1132
01:13:56.382 --> 01:14:00.553
and again and again
even if it is 10 years.


1133
01:14:00.586 --> 01:14:04.057
He always told me
nobody cared, always.


1134
01:14:06.359 --> 01:14:12.031
And one time he marched
in my room and he said:


1135
01:14:12.065 --> 01:14:14.600
"Told you nobody cared.

1136
01:14:14.634 --> 01:14:17.503
Your mom packed up
and moved to Florida."


1137
01:14:19.072 --> 01:14:23.843
There was never one candlelight
vigil for me. Okay?


1138
01:14:23.877 --> 01:14:25.812
[**]

1139
01:15:08.354 --> 01:15:09.789
[CARLA CLEARS THROAT]

1140
01:15:15.294 --> 01:15:17.096
Thank you.

1141
01:15:17.130 --> 01:15:20.299
[INDISTINCT CHATTER OVER TV]

1142
01:15:20.333 --> 01:15:24.237
I was beginning to think
the world was just all blurry.


1143
01:15:24.270 --> 01:15:28.007
Your therapist was here
again to see you.


1144
01:15:28.041 --> 01:15:31.110
I'm not--
I'm not ready yet, please.


1145
01:15:31.144 --> 01:15:32.846
REPORTER [ON TV]:
Ariel Castro standing
in the court


1146
01:15:32.879 --> 01:15:36.115
during the arraignment,
eyes cast down all the time


1147
01:15:36.149 --> 01:15:38.684
never looking up
at anyone.


1148
01:15:38.718 --> 01:15:40.486
No other reaction from the man.

1149
01:15:40.519 --> 01:15:42.956
Also with him
were his two brothers,


1150
01:15:42.989 --> 01:15:45.391
who have been eventually
released.


1151
01:15:45.424 --> 01:15:47.360
[**]

1152
01:15:49.295 --> 01:15:51.230
[INAUDIBLE DIALOGUE]

1153
01:16:34.707 --> 01:16:39.745
So when will I get to put Joey's
school picture in this frame?


1154
01:16:39.779 --> 01:16:42.548
Well, it's about waiting for
the adoption agency


1155
01:16:42.581 --> 01:16:44.183
to respond to our request.

1156
01:16:44.217 --> 01:16:46.652
You, um--
You gonna be okay here?


1157
01:16:46.685 --> 01:16:48.087
Yeah, am I gonna be okay?

1158
01:16:48.121 --> 01:16:51.490
A queen-size bed and all these
chairs to sit in just for me


1159
01:16:51.524 --> 01:16:54.828
for the first time in my life?
Yes, I'm gonna be great.


1160
01:16:54.861 --> 01:16:56.830
Well, then I'm glad
you're happy.


1161
01:16:56.863 --> 01:16:59.198
And I'll check in on you
as soon as I can.


1162
01:16:59.232 --> 01:17:00.333
Okay.

1163
01:17:04.503 --> 01:17:08.141
[DOOR OPENS THEN CLOSES]

1164
01:17:08.174 --> 01:17:10.109
[**]

1165
01:17:20.954 --> 01:17:24.557
MICHELLE:
I miss him so much.


1166
01:17:24.590 --> 01:17:27.460
It's like, what does
he even look like?


1167
01:17:27.493 --> 01:17:30.029
I wonder
if his name is still Joey.


1168
01:17:32.165 --> 01:17:38.471
Michelle, I've been
talking to my parents


1169
01:17:38.504 --> 01:17:41.340
and... I don't know.

1170
01:17:41.374 --> 01:17:44.210
Maybe I just...

1171
01:17:44.243 --> 01:17:48.147
I just need to start
living my normal life.


1172
01:17:48.181 --> 01:17:50.483
Just for right now.

1173
01:17:50.516 --> 01:17:52.886
What do you mean?
You can't just pretend


1174
01:17:52.919 --> 01:17:56.555
like this never happened
and go back.


1175
01:17:56.589 --> 01:18:01.127
Look, um, I'll see you
again soon, okay?


1176
01:18:01.160 --> 01:18:04.530
I promise.
Just not right away.


1177
01:18:04.563 --> 01:18:06.599
I'm sorry.

1178
01:18:06.632 --> 01:18:08.567
[**]

1179
01:18:12.138 --> 01:18:13.239
I love you.

1180
01:18:15.474 --> 01:18:17.043
I love you too.

1181
01:18:35.394 --> 01:18:37.063
[KNOCK ON DOOR]

1182
01:18:40.199 --> 01:18:41.968
Hi.
Hi.


1183
01:18:42.001 --> 01:18:43.469
So did you find Joey?

1184
01:18:43.502 --> 01:18:47.373
Um. I think maybe
you should sit down.


1185
01:18:48.841 --> 01:18:51.377
Joey's foster parents
adopted him


1186
01:18:51.410 --> 01:18:54.313
when he was 4 years old
and they've decided


1187
01:18:54.347 --> 01:18:57.883
that it's not in his best
interest to see you.


1188
01:18:59.919 --> 01:19:01.921
He's-
- He's doing well.

1189
01:19:01.955 --> 01:19:06.092
They just don't want any of
the commotion and attention


1190
01:19:06.125 --> 01:19:07.526
to upset his life.

1191
01:19:07.560 --> 01:19:09.295
But I'm not trying
to upset him.


1192
01:19:09.328 --> 01:19:11.197
I just wanted to hold
and hug him.


1193
01:19:11.230 --> 01:19:14.167
And just tell him that
I love him. Can I just do that?


1194
01:19:14.200 --> 01:19:17.536
Well, we raised the possibility
of a supervised visit.


1195
01:19:17.570 --> 01:19:21.374
They made it very clear on what
they thought was best for him.


1196
01:19:23.042 --> 01:19:25.578
Is his name
even Joey anymore?


1197
01:19:25.611 --> 01:19:28.181
I can't tell you that,
I'm sorry.


1198
01:19:29.648 --> 01:19:32.685
May I see a picture,
please?


1199
01:19:32.718 --> 01:19:35.955
I got the strong sense
that they're most comfortable


1200
01:19:35.989 --> 01:19:39.158
with no contact whatsoever.

1201
01:19:40.994 --> 01:19:43.496
I did talk to a family lawyer
I know.


1202
01:19:43.529 --> 01:19:46.365
According to him,
in a situation


1203
01:19:46.399 --> 01:19:50.003
where the birth mother
was not consulted


1204
01:19:50.036 --> 01:19:53.072
the adoption can be voided.

1205
01:19:53.106 --> 01:19:55.374
Would you talk to him
about that?


1206
01:19:55.408 --> 01:19:57.343
[**]

1207
01:20:04.583 --> 01:20:10.323
Do you mind if I have some
time by myself, please?


1208
01:20:16.895 --> 01:20:18.831
[SNIFFLING]

1209
01:20:22.335 --> 01:20:24.270
[SOBBING]

1210
01:20:30.176 --> 01:20:31.477
Michelle?
Hey.


1211
01:20:31.510 --> 01:20:33.779
I'm sorry if I'm intruding.
You know, I--


1212
01:20:33.812 --> 01:20:34.947
No, you're not.

1213
01:20:34.980 --> 01:20:37.183
I wanted to talk to you
about something.


1214
01:20:37.216 --> 01:20:38.417
Anything.

1215
01:20:39.885 --> 01:20:41.887
You know,
I always saw myself,


1216
01:20:41.920 --> 01:20:44.523
more than anything,
as Joey's mother.


1217
01:20:44.557 --> 01:20:45.891
Mm.

1218
01:20:45.924 --> 01:20:50.163
And I know that
I will be somebody.


1219
01:20:50.196 --> 01:20:52.065
But I don't want
a family lawyer.


1220
01:20:52.098 --> 01:20:55.768
You know, Joey,
he's happy now, you know?


1221
01:20:55.801 --> 01:20:57.236
He has a family
and a life.


1222
01:20:57.270 --> 01:20:59.438
And I don't wanna go
blowing that up.


1223
01:20:59.472 --> 01:21:02.641
It just doesn't feel right
to me.


1224
01:21:02.675 --> 01:21:04.377
You're sure?

1225
01:21:06.079 --> 01:21:08.347
Yeah.

1226
01:21:08.381 --> 01:21:12.818
It hurts like you wouldn't
believe, but I'm sure.


1227
01:21:12.851 --> 01:21:14.820
You're an amazing woman,
Michelle.


1228
01:21:14.853 --> 01:21:19.558
I don't know how amazing
I am, you know?


1229
01:21:19.592 --> 01:21:22.828
I don't even really know
how Michelle I am.


1230
01:21:24.663 --> 01:21:28.867
Maybe I am stronger
than I would have been


1231
01:21:28.901 --> 01:21:31.470
had I not gotten into
that truck, you know?


1232
01:21:31.504 --> 01:21:32.871
Mm.

1233
01:21:32.905 --> 01:21:37.410
I mean, I literally did not know
where I was going that day.


1234
01:21:39.112 --> 01:21:41.347
[SNIFFLING]

1235
01:21:41.380 --> 01:21:45.084
But that was the caterpillar,
you know?


1236
01:21:46.852 --> 01:21:52.525
And now I'm ready
for butterflies.


1237
01:21:52.558 --> 01:21:55.328
MAN [ON TV]:
And this was one
of the crimes of the century.


1238
01:21:55.361 --> 01:21:57.996
WOMAN:
Jeff, I want to ask you
about Michelle Knight


1239
01:21:58.030 --> 01:22:00.099
one of the victims
in this case.


1240
01:22:00.133 --> 01:22:04.637
She may appear in person in
the courtroom to give her say.


1241
01:22:04.670 --> 01:22:07.005
I find that unbelievably
courageous,


1242
01:22:07.039 --> 01:22:09.342
a woman who's been through
this hell.


1243
01:22:09.375 --> 01:22:12.711
Keep in mind, this man kept her
in a darkened room


1244
01:22:12.745 --> 01:22:14.147
for much of the time.

1245
01:22:14.180 --> 01:22:17.516
She was chained up.
Fed her once a day.


1246
01:22:17.550 --> 01:22:20.653
She became pregnant
and he...


1247
01:22:20.686 --> 01:22:22.621
[**]

1248
01:22:39.938 --> 01:22:41.707
CASTRO:
You're ugly.


1249
01:22:41.740 --> 01:22:46.679
You're stupid!
Nobody loves you!


1250
01:22:46.712 --> 01:22:49.215
Nobody's looking for you!

1251
01:22:50.516 --> 01:22:53.252
Gonna break your face!

1252
01:22:53.286 --> 01:22:57.490
You're not having my baby!
I hate you!


1253
01:23:00.659 --> 01:23:02.595
[REPORTERS CLAMORING]

1254
01:23:26.552 --> 01:23:29.455
MICHELLE:
My name is Michelle Knight,


1255
01:23:29.488 --> 01:23:33.459
and I would like to tell you
what this was like for me.


1256
01:23:33.492 --> 01:23:37.363
I missed my son every day

1257
01:23:37.396 --> 01:23:41.434
and I wondered if I was ever
gonna see him again.


1258
01:23:41.467 --> 01:23:46.171
I cried every night
because I was so alone.


1259
01:23:46.205 --> 01:23:48.040
[**]

1260
01:23:48.073 --> 01:23:50.976
The days never got shorter.

1261
01:23:51.009 --> 01:23:54.513
Days turned into nights,
and nights turned into days.


1262
01:23:54.547 --> 01:23:57.383
And the years turned
into eternity.


1263
01:23:57.416 --> 01:24:02.955
I knew at that point,
nobody cared about me.


1264
01:24:05.791 --> 01:24:08.060
Ariel Castro,

1265
01:24:09.862 --> 01:24:12.931
you took 11 years
of my life away.


1266
01:24:12.965 --> 01:24:16.269
